09:38.568 --> 09:40.991
We think things and wonder things like this.

09:41.352 --> 09:43.654
Am I praying the right way?

09:44.596 --> 09:48.340
We'll make statements like, I'm just not good at praying.

09:49.261 --> 09:50.863
Do I have the right words?

09:53.066 --> 09:56.210
Why does everything seem silent when I'm praying?

09:57.552 --> 09:59.915
Can I just say if you've ever felt that way?

10:01.257 --> 10:02.418
Welcome to the neighborhood.

10:04.386 --> 10:08.773
because you are surrounded with a group of people that feel much the same as you.

10:08.813 --> 10:20.692
In fact, I'm encouraged today because the disciples, the ones that walk side by side with Jesus for three and a half years, they also felt this way.

10:21.653 --> 10:22.334
