12:13.336 --> 12:17.780
So for the next few moments, I wanna look at the what, the why, and the how of prayer.

12:17.840 --> 12:30.514
Hang with me because I'm convinced that if we will truly engage in a life of prayer, listen carefully, then there's no stopping what God can and will do

12:30.850 --> 12:31.511
