12:33.294 --> 12:34.536
Come on.

12:34.556 --> 12:44.993
Every great revival that's ever existed began with a person kneeling their heart in their life and calling upon God.

12:46.235 --> 12:46.456
Why?

12:46.736 --> 12:47.858
Because prayer

12:48.130 --> 12:48.811
changes things.

12:49.051 --> 12:52.255
